OL,3,CRiver sees sewage pumped into it for
OL,4,Cmore than three weeks
OL,6,FThere are serious concerns sewage has
OL,7,Fbeen discharged into a Cotswold river
OL,8,Ffor more than 23 days straight ` and
OL,9,Fcounting.
OL,11,FThe Cotswolds Rivers Trust said a
OL,12,Fstorm overflow for the sewage
OL,13,Ftreatment works at Fairford has been
OL,14,Fdischarging into the River Coln
OL,15,Fcontinuously for more than 560 hours.
