OL,3,CRiver sees sewage pumped into it for
OL,4,Cmore than three weeks
OL,6,FIt started discharging untreated
OL,7,Fsewage on 23 September at 5.30am and
OL,8,Fhas done so every day since. The
OL,9,Fsecond storm overflow in the market
OL,10,Ftown has been out of action for more
OL,11,Fthan a month.
OL,13,FThe Cotswolds Rivers Trust is
OL,14,Fconcerned as it is not the first time
OL,15,Fthe failing sewage works in Fairford
OL,16,Fhave been in the news.
OL,18,FIn January, the Thames Water storm
OL,19,Foverflow pumped sewage into the Coln
OL,20,Ffor more than 900 hours.
