OL,3,CRiver sees sewage pumped into it for
OL,4,Cmore than three weeks
OL,6,F"Fairford Sewage Treatment Works storm
OL,7,Foverflow has now been discharging
OL,8,Funtreated sewage for over 500 hours
OL,9,Fstraight, meaning untreated sewage has
OL,10,Fbeen pouring continuously into the
OL,11,FRiver Coln for over 20 days," a
OL,12,FCotswolds Rivers Trust spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"The second storm overflow in Fairford
OL,16,Fhas not been working for about four
OL,17,Fweeks."
OL,19,FA Thames Water spokesperson said more
OL,20,Finvestment is needed across the entire
OL,21,Fwater company sector.
