OL,6,FIt added they have plans to upgrade
OL,7,F250 of their sites across the region
OL,8,Fincluding the sewage treatment works
OL,9,Fin Fairford.
OL,11,F"While all storm discharges are
OL,12,Funacceptable, the sewage system was
OL,13,Fhistorically designed to work in this
OL,14,Fway, to prevent sewage backing up into
OL,15,Fpeople's homes," they said.
