OL,6,F"We know how much people enjoy and
OL,7,Fappreciate rivers, and we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to seeing waterways thrive,
OL,9,Fbut we can't do it alone. Farming,
OL,10,Findustry, road runoff, wildlife and
OL,11,Fincreasingly extreme weather also play
OL,12,Fa role in river health.
OL,14,F"We have clear and deliverable plans
OL,15,Fto upgrade 250 of our sites across the
OL,16,Fregion, to increase treatment capacity
OL,17,Fand reduce the number of storm
OL,18,Fdischarges, including at our Fairford
OL,19,FSewage Treatment Works.
