OL,6,F"As infrastructure ages and demand on
OL,7,Fit increases more investment is needed
OL,8,Facross the entire sector That's why
OL,9,Fwe've asked for increased investment
OL,10,Fin the next regulatory cycle between
OL,11,F2025-2030.
OL,13,F"We've put transparency at the heart
OL,14,Fof what we do, and we were the first
OL,15,Fwater company to publish a real-time
OL,16,Fdata map on our website, which in its
OL,17,Ffirst year has been viewed over
OL,18,F350,000 times."
